- Tip: In react state management is controlled from one place https://youtu.be/hbLTt10nhOA?t=363
- There is 2 kind of input element in react: controlled and uncontrolled
- When we will provide value attribute in input element then it will be controlled element by React
- When we will not provide value attribute then it will be uncontrolled element and the state will be managed by DOM (browser)
- Tip: Input type=file is stateless, so it is always uncontrolled element
- Controlled elements are alsways best to handle form in react